{"tid":759524,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[慎入]《深宮計》收視報捷 總監製梅小青「半裸照」找數","createTime":"2018-07-28T16:29:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T03:09:30.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a788f808b01cd4376049f7180e20d55cfe647e8d","tid":759524,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T16:29:49.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】《宮心計2深宮計》收視報捷，一班演員早前在劇集點擊破30億時都陸續兌現承諾，紛紛貼出性感水著和裸照答找數，謝觀眾支持。總監製梅小青日前更揚言點擊破40億便會「找數」，更話自己已經找了一張半裸相為觀眾派福利：「不過就好多年前喇！」<br />\n<br />\n64歲的梅小青昨在Facebook找數，「大家開心地找數了，何離（蕭正楠）也要我找數，我爽快的答應了，而且不是放童年照的，不過不知道是誰發明找數的？」<br />\n<br />\n不少粉絲大讚梅小青索爆，「嘩，索呀」、「殺死人咩」、「嘩！怪不得家豪哥每次望住你都笑咪咪啦」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/uIMw1WMj0jKQG3iWT4l4hg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20180728f104429.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FuIMw1WMj0jKQG3iWT4l4hg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20180728f104429.jpg&h=bbcf3c5d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9938c42d8eaa67212fbda7b44b37a02683faf13e","tid":759524,"uid":48905,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T16:30:43.000Z","msg":"有無梅小惠半裸照？"},{"pid":"fe5638926d16c060ae0f65f3742a148e2c30f543","tid":759524,"uid":10277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T16:31:19.000Z","msg":"嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c3c0183ee3ed37e3f8856d74fd5c694e40eae15","tid":759524,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T16:36:25.000Z","msg":"不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fed259aea0068374e8bc847deda6b4c106c1f09","tid":759524,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":0